課程教材 Course Material
	    Every student is assigned to select more than one paper of his/her interest for all the classmates to critique and discussion. However, the student who selects the article must prepare 8-10 slides of background knowledge for all classmates to read it before they actually read through the selected paper.The process of critique follows the principles outlined in the Chapter 14 of Professor Wang's Chinese textbook of 流行病學方法論修訂版    

參考書目 References
	    王榮德：流行病學方法論修訂版，臺北：臺大醫學院出版委員會，2010。(Or, Wang JD. Basic principles and practical applications in epidemiological research. Singapore: World Scientific, 2002.)    

